               <history>
                  <origin>
                     
                     <origDate notBefore="1598" notAfter="1674">According to the colophon, the unit
                        was written in 250 year of mercy (= 1674 A.D.). It could be dated back also
                        to 1598 A.D. (if the date is calculated according to the cicle of martyrs);
                        this earlier date would better match the palaeographic features attested for
                        hand a.</origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>The name of the original donors have been
                     erased throughout the Ms. and often crudely replaced with that of Qǝddǝsta
                     Krǝstos and Tasfā Mikāʾel (see also Additio 6). Besides, many other names have
                     been added in the same more recent hand: Walatta Dǝngǝl (<locus target="#23rb">23rb</locus>), Walatta Qāl (<locus target="#24va">24va</locus>, 25vb),
                     Walda Krǝstos (<locus target="#26va">26va</locus>), and others.</provenance>
               </history>
               
